asset.author: Nike
asset.hookText:
To celebrate the start of 2013, @NikeNYC invited runners from
all over the 5 boroughs to a celebration at Niketown NY, followed by a
midnight run. As the ball dropped, the pack stormed across the starting line and into a new year of shattered goals and counted miles. The mission: #makeitcount in 2013. Together.
